OL,3,CPakistan will be represented in
OL,4,CHundred cricket tournament
OL,6,FPakistan will be represented at this
OL,7,Fsummer's Hundred tournament after
OL,8,Fspinner Usman Tariq was signed by
OL,9,FBirmingham Phoenix at the inaugural
OL,10,Fmen's auction.
OL,12,FThe Hundred tournament is a 100-ball
OL,13,Fcricket competition in the UK,
OL,14,Ffeaturing world-class players split
OL,15,Finto eight city-based teams.
OL,17,FThis year, players are selected
OL,18,Fthrough a new auction system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
