OL,3,CPakistan will be represented in
OL,4,CHundred cricket tournament
OL,6,FThe England and Wales Cricket Board
OL,7,Fhas issued formal denials of an
OL,8,Feffective 'shadow ban' being employed
OL,9,Fby some of the sides that have taken
OL,10,FIndian investment.
OL,12,FThe Board released a joint statement
OL,13,Ffrom all eight franchises affirming
OL,14,Fthat players would not be excluded on
OL,15,Fnationality.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
