OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773342677
OL,3,CPakistan will be represented in
OL,4,CHundred cricket tournament
OL,6,FThe country's only female
OL,7,Frepresentatives, Fatima Sana and Sadia
OL,8,FIqbal, went unsold in the women's
OL,9,Fauction, Shaheen Shah Afridi withdrew
OL,10,Ffrom the men's sale on Wednesday
OL,11,Fevening, and fellow quick Haris Rauf
OL,12,Ffailed to attract an offer when he was
OL,13,Fput up for his reserve price of
OL,14,F#100,000.
OL,16,FThere will have been relief at the ECB
OL,17,Fthat Tariq, who bowls with an
OL,18,Funorthodox stop-start action, was sold
OL,19,Ffor #140,000 after a brief tussle
OL,20,Fbetween the Phoenix and Trent Rockets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
