OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773342677
OL,3,CPakistan will be represented in
OL,4,CHundred cricket tournament
OL,6,FIt is equally notable that both groups
OL,7,Fhave American co-owners, with none of
OL,8,Fthose affiliated to Indian backers
OL,9,Fjoining the bidding.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FLast year's tournament MVP Jordan Cox
OL,17,Flanded the biggest deal among the
OL,18,Fmarquee English contingent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
