OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773342677
OL,3,CPakistan will be represented in
OL,4,CHundred cricket tournament
OL,6,FHe picked up #300,000 from Welsh Fire
OL,7,Fin the first round at London's
OL,8,FPiccadilly Lights. They then spent a
OL,9,Ffurther #240,000 on Test star Joe
OL,10,FRoot, shelling out more than half
OL,11,Ftheir budget on two of the first three
OL,12,Fplayers.
OL,14,FAll eight franchises entered the
OL,15,Fbidding hall with just over #1million
OL,16,Fat their disposal to build their
OL,17,Fsquads, with each already locking in
OL,18,Ffour players apiece as direct
OL,19,Fsignings, and the Cardiff-based outfit
OL,20,Fspent big in the opening minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
